the fight
over nominating Justice Antonin
Scalia's successor.

00:17.117 --> 00:23.257 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Also ahead this
Wednesday: Apple
opposes a judge's order to
unlock the iPhone

00:23.357 --> 00:28.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
