shooters, saying
the ruling would undermine
customers' privacy.

00:28.762 --> 00:30.430 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And:

00:30.530 --> 00:32.232 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ADRIAAN VLOK, Former South
African Minister
of Law and Order: I am guilty. I
am sorry.

00:32.332 --> 00:34.101 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Will you please forgive me?

00:34.201 --> 00:39.206 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: A story of
reconciliation:
how an apartheid-era police
official is now

00:39.306 --> 00:41.208 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
