brutalized.

00:41.308 --> 00:46.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DINAH SEKESE, Volunteer Relief
Worker: And
they say, can you believe
Adriaan Vlok can

00:46.246 --> 00:53.053 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
