changed.

00:55.355 --> 00:58.792 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: All that and more on
tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

00:58.892 --> 01:03.263 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
