producers to pump

05:32.966 --> 05:34.768 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
less.

05:34.868 --> 05:38.305 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Despite Iran's
statement, the
price of oil traded higher
today, and that

05:38.405 --> 05:45.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
