industrial average gained 257
points to close

05:45.111 --> 05:52.219 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
near 16454. The Nasdaq rose 98
points, and
the S&amp;P 500 added 31.

05:52.319 --> 05:58.725 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And there's a new
top dog in the
land. A German shorthaired
pointer named C.J.

05:58.825 --> 06:04.431 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
took best in show last night at
the Westminster
Dog Show in New York. The
3-year-old champion

06:04.531 --> 06:11.137 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
