17:26.913 --> 17:29.415 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES COMEY, FBI Director: We
still have one
of those killers' phones that we
have not

17:29.515 --> 17:33.185 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
