17:33.286 --> 17:37.990 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Last week, FBI
Director James
Comey told a Senate hearing that
the Apple

17:38.090 --> 17:44.330 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
iPhone's encryption has made it
