to unlock any iPhone in
someone's physical

18:07.653 --> 18:09.488 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
possession."

18:09.588 --> 18:14.493 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
White House Press Secretary Josh
Earnest disputed
that, saying the government
wants access only

18:14.593 --> 18:17.330 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
