This is a much more specific
request that

18:32.812 --> 18:34.714 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the Department of Justice has
put forward.

18:34.814 --> 18:40.353 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Apple stepped up its
protections
after NSA leaker Edward Snowden
exposed government

18:40.453 --> 18:44.123 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
