not building a permanent back
door into anything.

19:58.064 --> 20:01.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's one phone, one order, one
security
feature.

20:01.600 --> 20:05.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: So, Nate Cardozo, if
