20:31.497 --> 20:37.103 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, when you hear Stewart or the
White House
press secretary say it's only
this one phone,

20:37.203 --> 20:38.604 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
