20:38.704 --> 20:41.474 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Well, are we talking
about precedent
here, Stewart Baker?

20:41.574 --> 20:48.114 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEWART BAKER: Well, there is
longstanding
precedent, 200 years old, that
says that if

20:48.214 --> 20:54.353 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
