49:19.723 --> 49:29.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: I thought they
would be capable
of the fluidity that would seem
feminine,

49:29.133 --> 49:33.971 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and also appropriate to the look
of the film.

49:34.071 --> 49:43.013 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: This is before we
have even
met the two women in the film.
Right?

49:43.113 --> 49:44.281 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: Exactly, right.

49:44.381 --> 49:45.850 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So you have
introduced the
characters.

49:45.950 --> 49:49.787 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: That's right. I
have introduced
-- that's right, exactly.

49:49.887 --> 49:54.225 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Another example,
this time
with the piano filling in the
dialogue, comes

49:54.325 --> 49:58.362 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
