women drive
to "Carol"'s house.

49:58.462 --> 50:04.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: The left hand of
the piano
is playing a rhythm, but it goes
into these

50:05.002 --> 50:10.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
