crystal-clear,
and sort of pointillistic, and
very simple.

50:18.649 --> 50:22.620 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And we're inside
a different
universe now, right, in the car.

50:22.720 --> 50:26.757 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: Exactly, and the
