50:33.230 --> 50:39.570 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: With "Carol,"
Burwell had eight
weeks to craft the music, but,
in this world,

50:39.670 --> 50:41.505 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
