50:41.605 --> 50:46.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: It's deadline
composing. That's
-- there are a lot of qualities
that maybe

50:46.210 --> 50:52.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
