storytelling.

51:01.191 --> 51:07.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARTER BURWELL: As a viewer and
listener,
I prefer to be a little less
informed. I prefer

51:07.598 --> 51:13.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
